arch c_sage
msg
@match clock
A pretty nice clock, he ? It is really a rare antiquity. It was built in Euthville, during the golden age of that city. Can you imagine ? That clock is hundreds of years old !
We found it in the ruins of the city long ago, and my brother fixed it. My brother was a genius...
*sigh*
@match Euthville
It was an city located at the north of Scorn, where people could build wonderful machines one can only dream of nowadays. But their thirst for power killed them; today, only ruins remain from Euthville.
@match brother
My brother Keiran and I always were pretty close. When the armies of Kurthan the Bloody took Wolfsburg, I managed to escape, but my brother didn't, and was put into slavery.
I really don't know if he's still alive or not. That clock is the only souvenir I have from the happy times of our youth...
*sigh*
@match *
I'm Heinkel Heimser. What do you want from an old man like me ?
*sigh*
endmsg
x 2
y 4
end
